      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Originalists would counter that their methodology is inherently neutral because it anchors interpretation to objective historical data, not subjective judicial preference. They argue that any judge who selectively chooses which historical documents or contemporary understandings to prioritize is simply injecting bias. Therefore, the appearance of political agenda is a misunderstanding of the commitment to fidelity to the text as understood by the framers.",
